# LFS attributes intentionally removed — all *.db / *.abcddb files in this
# repo are synthetic fixtures generated locally on `pnpm install` (and
# gitignored). Auto-LFS-tracking *.db would silently push 50MB+ of synthetic
# fixture data to LFS storage on every accidental commit.
#
# These explicit `-filter -diff -merge` patterns prevent a future contributor
# (or `git lfs track "*.db"` invocation) from accidentally re-enabling LFS on
# DB blobs. If you genuinely need LFS for a specific path, tag that path
# narrowly, not the whole pattern.
*.db -filter -diff -merge text
*.abcddb -filter -diff -merge text
